gomodel:SYNGO_4911  a    owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment     "Rationale: Figure 6G-H: KCNQ2 immunogold labeling in the primate dorsolateral prefrontal cortex showed localization at dendritic spines and dendrites. The omission of the primary antibody or substitution with non-immune serum abolished all reactivity.\n\nBased on the known transmembrane topology of this protein, \"integral component of ... membrane\" term was selected.. Experimental description: Brain tissue from four adult Rhesus macaques (10-22 y.o., female)\nKCNQ2 antibody: Abcam, Cat # ab22897; RRID:AB_775890" , "Automated change 2024-03-14: GO:0099055 replaced by GO:0045211" ;
